OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPersistent
OL,6,Fevening rain and drizzle will clear
OL,7,Feast overnight with mostly dry
OL,8,Fconditions and occasional clear spells
OL,9,Ffollowing, although a few showers are
OL,10,Flikely to arrive across the Pennines.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FSunny spells and isolated
OL,13,Fshowers, these most likely across the
OL,14,FPennines, until late afternoon. Then
OL,15,Ffrequent showers will spread east,
OL,16,Flocally heavy with a small chance of
OL,17,Fhail and thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
